quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"Praise be to Allah, Lord of the Worlds"
  1,2,"The Beneficent, the Merciful"
  1,3,Master of the Day of Judgment
  1,4,Thee (alone) we worship; Thee (alone) we ask for help
  1,5,Show us the straight path
  1,6,The path of those whom Thou hast favoured; Not the (path) of those who earn Thine anger nor of those who go astray